<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
    .content { line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Invoice App!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining Invoice App! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
      <p>With Invoice App, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create and manage professional invoices</li>
        <li>Track payments</li>
        <li>Manage customers</li>
        <li>Generate reports</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
      </p>
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Invoice App Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 